Congo’s Inflation Rate Increased to 18.35% as of July 3, Central Bank Says

-- B y   M i c h a e l   J .   K a v a n a g h
-- 
2011-07-05T08:29:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-05/congo-s-inflation-rate-increased-to-18-35-as-of-july-3-central-bank-says.html
Democratic Republic of Congo’s
inflation rate rose to 18.35 percent as of July 3 from 17.99
percent a week earlier, the central bank said.  Prices increased 2.07 percent for the month of June, the
Kinshasa-based central bank said on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michael J. Kavanagh in Kinshasa at 
 mkavanagh9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
